        "subject": "LU-7566 lnet: add “quiet” parameter to parse_nidrange()",
        "message": "LU-7566 lnet: add “quiet” parameter to parse_nidrange()\n\nWhile mounting Lustre servers, cfs_parse_nidlist() outputs\nbogus “can't parse nidrange” errors to the console. This\npatch fixes the issue by adding a “quiet” parameter to\nparse_nidrange() and also making lmd_parse_nidlist()\ncall cfs_parse_nidlist_quiet().\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I7e36111f6b6592de5d55b73197322303030e72c2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
